###Kyklo Zwhs tou Kyttarou

-To xroniko diasthma pou mesolavei apo th dhmiourgeia enos kyttarou ews kai pou to idio 8a
8a paragei tous apogwnous tou. 

Xwrizetai se dyo phases.

-A: Mesofash

	-G1 (First Gap):
		Inidia Xrwmatinhs
		1 inidio xrwamtinhs
		1 morio DNA
		Biosyn8esh mRNA, tRNA, riboswmatwn kai proteinwn (domikwn kai leitourgikwn) 

	-S (Synthesis):
		Inidia Xrwmatinhs
		1 inidio xrwmatinhs
		2 moria DNA
		Autodiplasiasmos Gennetikou Ylikoy

	-G2 (Second Gap):
		Inidia Xrwmatinhs
		1 inidio xrwmatinhs
		2 moria DNA
		Diairesh mitoxondriwn, xlorplastwn kai kentroswmatiou (opou yparxei)
		(ta xrwmoswmata den einai diakrita akoma logw xamhlou ba8mou symphknwshs)

-B: Mitwtikh Diairesh/Mitwsh -> Xrwmoswmata
	-Profash
	-Metafrash
	-Anafash
	-Telofash


***H Mesofash (A) antiproswpevei to 90-95% ths diarkeias tou kyttarikou kyklou. Kata th 
diarkeia ths, ta kyttara fainetai na <<adranoun>> giati den parathrountai entona 
kinhtika fainomena sto xwro tou pyrhna. Sth pragmatikothta omws apotelei periodo aujhshs
ogkou tou kyttarou & periodo proetoimasias tou kyttarou gia thn epikeimenh diairesh tou.
Auto ka8orizei entones metabolikes diadikasies (diplasiasmo DNA, syn8esh mRNA, tRNA,
prwteinwn).


###Kyttarikh Diairesh

-A Dixotomhsh (stous prokarywtikous organismous Ex. bakthria)
	-Den exoun xrwmoswmata/pyrhnes

-B Mitwsh (eukarywtika kyttara -> swmatika)

-C Meiwsh (paragwgh gametwn -> mono sta awra gennhtika kyttara)


-Pou xrhsimevei h kyttarikh diairesh:

(*) H monogonikh anaparagwgh twn organismwn (Dixotomhsh)

(*) H amfigonikh anaparagwgh twn organismwn mesw thn synenwshs twn gametwn (Meiwsh)

(*) H aujhsh twn kyttarwn & h anaptyjh polykyttarwn organismwn (Mitwsh)

(*) H antikatastash twn nekrwn, katestrammenwn h ghrasmenwn kyttarwn stous istous 
me alla omoia me auta. (Mitwsh) 
